  "title": "instanceof 继承",
  "group": "类型检查技巧",
  "options": [
    {
      "text": "true, true, true"
    },
    {
      "text": "true, false, false"
    },
    {
      "text": "false, true, true"
    },
    {
      "text": "true, true, false"
    }
  ],
  "objectives": [],
  "questionProse": [
    "这些检查的结果是什么？"
  ],
  "hintsProse": [
    "记住JavaScript继承中的原型链。"
  ],
  "explanationProse": [
    "三个都返回`true`。`CustomError`继承自`Error`，而`Error`又继承自`Object`。`instanceof`运算符会检查整个原型链，因此`CustomError`实例同时也是`Error`和`Object`的实例。"
  ]
}
